"@label, %1 is the total amount of installed system memory, %2 is the amount "
"of which is usable, both expressed as 7.7 GiB"
msgid "%1 of RAM (%2 usable)"
msgstr "%1 ئەسلەك (%2 ئىشلىتىلىشچان)"

#: MemoryEntry.cpp:137
#, kde-format
